    "INSTRUCTION: Identify 3 people who have made significant contributions to the field of robotics.",
    "Masahiro Mori: Masahiro Mori is a Japanese roboticist and researcher, widely known for his pioneering work in robotics and humanrobot interaction.",
    "He is most famous for creating the concept of the \"uncanny valley,\"which describes the discomfort people feel when a robot or animation looks and moves almost, but not exactly, like a natural human being. 2.",
